features: 【Large Capacity 6-Tier Shoe Rack】Our metal vertical shoe storage shelves' height of a single shelf is about 7.9 inches, one tier can store 3-4 pairs of shoes. You can remove the third fabric shelf layer to place your tall boots. And the bottom tier is off the ground with extra space for flats, such as slippers, loafers and flip flops, etc. Perfect space is more suitable for you to organize.

【Modern & Adjustable Shoe Rack】 Unique adjustable feet design can make the shoe shelf organizer keep balance on uneven floors. The top wooden board has an extra benefit to hold your bags, books and other items, enough decorative and rustic look easier to match your home.

【Multi-scenario Use】 A multi-functional standing shoe rack to increase vertical use space, as an entry shoe rack or closet shoe rack, bedroom shoe rack or front door shoes, it has been a lifesaver in keeping your shoes off the floor or in a pile in a corner.

【Stronger & Durable】 The shoe organizer is made of thickened metal tubes and fabric (Not a Wooden Top), square side frame makes the shoe shelf stronger, stainless steel X shaped reinforcement on the side of the shoe rack reinforces it.
【Easy to Assemble Shoe Storage Rack】 It comes with everything you need to assemble, easy to read directions and labeled pieces, just spend about 15 minutes by hand to build free standing shoe racks.

reviews.reviewText: Very happy with this purchase. No BS assembly. Easy, my 3 yr old and I didn’t it together. I did install the dang cloth columns upside down, but no one can tell and I wasn’t about to take it apart 😆. Sturdy and good looking. Love it. Buy it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars worked to great!
reviews.reviewText: I wasn't expecting the sturdiness to be as good as it was cause of the price point. Shocked a bit how well it was acctually, still looks great! I love it it helps our entrie look so much better. It came with two hooks as well, say to put one on each side (maybe so the weight isn't to heavy on one side). But we put both on one side and just used them for light weight stuff. A nice little bonus. I had a hard time picking how many shelves I wanted at first, until I noticed this one had the option to slant the lower shelves or not. I choose to slant all but the first one use that to hold random stuff. The top shelf wood is nice for photos or a plant. I was a little disappointed that the wood is two pieces not just one big one. They didnt line up as good but you wont notice unless you built it or it was pointed out. So not a huge deal. The rest shelves I have our shoes on and cleared up the clutter by the front door. We love it!! Thank you! (tried to post a picture but wont accept the pic)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 8, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Tall shoe rack for small space
reviews.reviewText: I have a very small mud room, where I keep all my shoes. I love how this shoe rack fits perfectly in the corner of it. The height of the rack allows for alot of shoe storage. One of the adjustable shelves even lets me store boots. It does take a little time to put together as it has alot of small pieces and components. It is worth the effort because it will fit neatly in most small areas, still hold a decent amount of shoes and looks very stylish. Very good buy, can't ask for much else.
